APPENDIX.P:
3.1. Angle-measuring Device Rotational Offset (R
              ADO
              ). The rotational position of an angle-measuring device relative to the reference scribe line, as determined during the pre-test rotational position check described in section 8.3.

3.15 Reference Scribe Line Rotational Offset (R
              SLO
              ). The rotational position of a probe's reference scribe line relative to the probe's yaw-null position, as determined during the yaw angle calibration described in section 10.5.

